          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two exposures were made.  In the first, the 1.4-MeV",
                "deuteron beam interacted with nitrogen target gas at  a",
                "pressure of 8-mm Hg.  In the 2.4-MeV exposure, an air",
                "target at approximately the same pressure was used.",
                "For both exposures, the gas scattering gap was enclosed",
                "by aluminium foils 0.1-mg/cm**2 thick in order to",
                "prevent emulsion figging."
              ]
            }
          ],
