          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors.  The absolute cross sections for the",
                "various charged particle groupes observed in the work",
                "can not be measured directly because of uncertainties",
                "in the measurement of the total beam charge.",
                "-By compiler. The authors could not determine absolute",
                "cross sections directly. Therefore compiler assumed the",
                "data as relative ones."
